'''Gilded dragonhide armour''' offers similar offensive bonuses and notably higher defensive bonuses than the [[green dragonhide armour]], and is a possible reward from completing [[Clue scroll (elite)|elite]] [[Treasure Trails]].

While most pieces of the armour are available in the [[free-to-play]] worlds, the coif is a [[members]]-only item.

